{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/EN-titleIntro.png?t=1737888654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hi, I'm KoKo. I'm the new order picker at AmaZoo.\u00a0</strong>My job is to get these boxes to the right place\u2014or at least, I <i>think</i> it is. I don\u2019t have all the instructions yet, and there are some dangerous things around here that I\u2019m not too sure about. <strong>Can you help me move all these boxes and find the way out?</strong> I really can\u2019t wait for this long day to be over!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/EN-titleGameplay.png?t=1737888654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/giff_gameplay_Steam.gif?t=1737888654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>AmaZoo is a progressive and varied puzzle game</strong>, inspired by the classic Sokoban, but reimagined in a side-view perspective reminiscent of old-school 2D games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With <strong>simple mouse-only controls</strong>, you\u2019ll enjoy an intuitive experience as you <strong>solve over 100 puzzles</strong> across multiple stages, each designed to <strong>challenge your logical thinking</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your task is to <strong>move and organize different types of boxes to clear the path to the exit</strong> and advance to the next stage. But watch out\u2014some boxes behave unpredictably, and one wrong step could turn a simple task into a tricky challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/EN-titleBoxes.png?t=1737888654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/boxes.png?t=1737888654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are several types of \u2018boxes\u2019 in the game, each with unique characteristics and mechanisms. As KoKo, you\u2019ll need to use your skills to <strong>carry, drop, throw, stack, jump, and climb with the boxes in hand</strong>. And if one gets in your way or drives you crazy, <strong>don\u2019t hesitate to kick it out of your path!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/EN-titleTrap.png?t=1737888654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>AmaZoo\u2019s warehouses are anything but safe</strong>\u2014definitely not up to humanoid safety standards. You\u2019ll encounter towering staircases, compactors, faulty machinery, spikes, lasers, and even explosive hazards. <strong>Be careful, KoKo\u2014workplace accidents are just around the corner!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/extras/EN-titleExperience.png?t=1737888654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don\u2019t let the calm atmosphere fool you\u2014<strong>progression brings increasingly challenging puzzles designed to push your logic and creativity to the limit.</strong> Will you rise to the occasion?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you enjoy a challenge, you can replay levels to beat your own record! <strong>But remember: optimizing your work is key.</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066360/page_bg_generat